Class SnakeTree

java.lang.Object
  SnakeTree

public class SnakeTree
extends java.lang.Object

SnakeTree is a Tree made up of SnakeNode nodes Each node contains a Snake object.

The tree can be iterated with a SnakeTree.SnakeTreeIterator, returned by getIterator()

Version:
1.0
Author:
Niall Deasy
See Also:
Snake, SnakeNode, SnakeTree.SnakeTreeIterator
